{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/common-responses.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Common responses provide consistent messaging across the platform and prevent you from having to write out the same message again and again. When you select an action for a report, you can have a common response pre-populate for that specific action.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"common-response-1\"\n        title=\"common-response-1\"\n        src=\"/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/0b533/common-response-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/fac75/common-response-1.png 125w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/63868/common-response-1.png 250w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/0b533/common-response-1.png 500w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/1d69c/common-response-1.png 750w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/00d43/common-response-1.png 1000w,\n/static/ced4e441b06b9700e682acbe9f55a2c6/97a96/common-response-1.png 2400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"set-up-a-default-common-response\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#set-up-a-default-common-response\" aria-label=\"set up a default common response permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Set Up a Default Common Response</h3>\n<p>To set a default common response:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <b>Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses</b>.</li>\n<li>You'll find a pre-populated list of responses that HackerOne finds useful.</li>\n<li>Click the <b>Set default Common Responses</b> button.</li>\n<li>In the <b>Default Common Responses</b> window, select the default response message from the drop-down next to the action.</li>\n<li>Click <b>Save</b>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The default common response will automatically populate when you select the action for the report.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 493px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 142.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"common-response-2\"\n        title=\"common-response-2\"\n        src=\"/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/f88d0/common-response-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/fac75/common-response-2.png 125w,\n/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/63868/common-response-2.png 250w,\n/static/b41177b2146cb7c7403ec0a6ac320c4d/f88d0/common-response-2.png 493w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"add-your-own-common-response\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#add-your-own-common-response\" aria-label=\"add your own common response permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Add Your Own Common Response</h3>\n<p>You can write your own common response. To add a new common response:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses</strong>.</li>\n<li>Select the <strong>Add Common Response</strong> button.</li>\n<li>Type the title of your response in the <strong>Common Response Title</strong> field. This title will show up in the list of common responses to choose from.</li>\n<li>Type the message of your response in the <strong>Message</strong> field.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Create Common Response</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Your common response will display in the list of common responses to choose from when you set up a default common response.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"common-response-3\"\n        title=\"common-response-3\"\n        src=\"/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/0b533/common-response-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/fac75/common-response-3.png 125w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/63868/common-response-3.png 250w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/0b533/common-response-3.png 500w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/1d69c/common-response-3.png 750w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/00d43/common-response-3.png 1000w,\n/static/5e672cd6b30d2969cfd35acd58c54372/6f464/common-response-3.png 1464w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"edit-a-common-response\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#edit-a-common-response\" aria-label=\"edit a common response permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Edit a Common Response</h3>\n<p>To edit a common response:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Settings > Program > Automation > Common Responses</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click the title of the response you want to edit.</li>\n<li>Edit the title and the message.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Update Common Response</strong>.</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/common-responses.html","id":"programs/common-responses","title":"Common Responses","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Set Up a Default Common Response"},{"value":"Add Your Own Common Response"},{"value":"Edit a Common Response"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}